which is very interesting.

00:18:55.975 --> 00:18:59.881
Some money has definitely
come into this town for a place this size.

00:18:59.948 --> 00:19:03.059
That is a sweet looking library
I gotta say.

00:19:03.800 --> 00:19:05.136
And then what is this?

00:19:05.203 --> 00:19:09.130
The University of Arkansas Pine Bluff
Business Support Incubator

00:19:09.197 --> 00:19:10.804
and Office Complex.

00:19:11.283 --> 00:19:13.923
Let's go in this library
and get a look-see.

00:19:19.260 --> 00:19:21.756
Yeah so quite impressive I gotta say.

00:19:22.180 --> 00:19:24.878
And just literally a stone's throw

00:19:25.606 --> 00:19:27.855
from those buildings that are falling down,

00:19:27.922 --> 00:19:29.183
you have this.

00:19:29.250 --> 00:19:31.765
And as a creator I want to tell you guys.

00:19:31.832 --> 00:19:35.260
I could come into this town,
just focus purely on the blight.

00:19:35.830 --> 00:19:39.223
Probably have a more viral video doing so.

00:19:39.670 --> 00:19:42.863
Because it's maybe more interesting
than the library.

00:19:42.930 --> 00:19:46.165
But I want to be as fair as possible
to the locals here.

00:19:47.048 --> 00:19:50.712
But also to you, the audience,
because right now on the Internet

00:19:50.779 --> 00:19:54.708
the model of extremes works pretty good.

00:19:55.146 --> 00:19:58.969
And, you know,
libraries aren't what people click on.

00:20:08.700 --> 00:20:10.288
I don't know what this was.

00:20:12.120 --> 00:20:14.136
Look at the size of this place.

00:20:17.208 --> 00:20:19.095
Nice I-beam construction here.

00:20:20.318 --> 00:20:21.906
It's probably too far gone.

00:20:24.323 --> 00:20:28.482
All right guys. I was told
there's a place called Rich's Burgers.

00:20:29.240 --> 00:20:30.309
