00:20:37.000 --> 00:20:39.923
Trying to get there before
it shuts down.

00:20:40.990 --> 00:20:42.814
You know that woman in the shop

00:20:43.345 --> 00:20:45.657
was scared when she saw me.

00:20:45.724 --> 00:20:47.750
