00:23:40.340 --> 00:23:41.842
Arkansas is a wonderful state.

00:23:41.909 --> 00:23:44.430
I've only been here two days.
Everyone's very nice.

00:23:44.497 --> 00:23:47.459
That's our biggest asset right now
is our population.

00:23:47.526 --> 00:23:49.900
There are some fine people lived here.

00:23:49.967 --> 00:23:51.695
-And your name ma'am?
-Betty Motes.

00:23:51.762 --> 00:23:53.280
Betty Motes. Okay.

00:23:53.347 --> 00:23:55.410
