-Seven dollars.

00:25:03.962 --> 00:25:07.258
Okay so under ten bucks
you can eat a great meal.

00:25:07.325 --> 00:25:10.090
Oh under ten dollars
you get what you got there.

00:25:11.181 --> 00:25:13.088
