Man, all I got to say is
we hope that change comes here.

01:03:06.475 --> 01:03:09.122
It could get worse than this,
but we hope not.

01:03:09.675 --> 01:03:11.899
But we hope that it changes and

01:03:12.589 --> 01:03:16.489
the community gets built back up
and businesses come back in.

01:03:17.035 --> 01:03:18.730
That's all we can hope for.

01:03:18.803 --> 01:03:22.414
People like Peter coming here
and putting Pine Bluff on the map…

01:03:22.481 --> 01:03:25.177
-…when it's got such a bad rap for so long.
-Okay.

01:03:25.244 --> 01:03:28.769
I think that it might do some good here.
So…

01:03:29.323 --> 01:03:30.985
-Well, I met great people today.

01:03:31.052 --> 01:03:32.736
-Yeah.
-Awesome people.

01:03:32.809 --> 01:03:35.011
Thank you all
to the Pine Bluffians out there

01:03:35.078 --> 01:03:37.038
who got on camera, told your story.

01:03:37.560 --> 01:03:39.175
And thank you, Alex.

01:03:39.242 --> 01:03:40.803
That was awesome.

01:03:40.870 --> 01:03:44.333
And guys,
I have a whole Arkansas series here.

01:03:44.400 --> 01:03:46.983
-The next video, I'm going to Bentonville.
-Oh, wow.

01:03:47.050 --> 01:03:51.029
-Which is a totally different Arkansas.
-Yeah, absolutely. You're gonna love it.

01:03:51.096 --> 01:03:53.668
-Other side of the tracks, right?
-Yup. Absolutely.

01:03:53.735 --> 01:03:56.334
And if you want to see
my first Arkansas video,

01:03:56.401 --> 01:03:59.611
Arkansas first impressions,
I shot that in Little Rock.

01:03:59.678 --> 01:04:00.975
That was awesome.

01:04:01.042 --> 01:04:02.646
That should be around here.

01:04:02.713 --> 01:04:05.163
Thanks for coming along
on that journey, you guys.

01:04:05.230 --> 01:04:06.578
Until the next one.

01:04:06.645 --> 01:04:09.116
-Now you're part of it, Alex.
-Thanks, man.

01:04:09.182 --> 01:04:10.451
[jazz music]

